      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GINGER RUSH (4) comes off an average run last start when seventh at Hobart over 340m behind Bundaberg Gum (19.89) in a Grade 4. Was in the money prior to that. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Looks the one to beat on her best form. PRISTINE (2) finished fourth last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 278m at this track, taking a Special conditions race in a blistering 15.99. Smart winner two back and looks a key chance on that form. WANAKA (1) could manage only second last time but ran speedy time (19.38) at Hobart over 340m when beaten 3 lengths in a Grade 3/4. In form and looks a leading player again. GOOD LUCK BABE (3) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
